### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = SEU_TOKEN_JWT_AQUI
@movieId = ID_DO_FILME_AQUI

### 1. Criar um filme para testar
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Teste Upload Imagens",
  "releaseDate": "2025-12-31T00:00:00.000Z",
  "rating": 8.5,
  "genre": "Ação"
}

### 2. Upload de Poster
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/poster
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="poster.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/your/poster.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 3. Upload de Backdrop
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}/backdrop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="backdrop.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/your/backdrop.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 4. Verificar se as URLs foram salvas
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{movieId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# ALTERNATIVA: Usando cURL (copie e cole no terminal)

# Upload Poster
curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/movies/SEU_MOVIE_ID/poster \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN" \
  -F "file=@./caminho/para/poster.jpg"

# Upload Backdrop
curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/movies/SEU_MOVIE_ID/backdrop \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN" \
  -F "file=@./caminho/para/backdrop.jpg"
